yingyinNormal.en: Pizza delivery. I'll get it. I will get that.
yingyinNormal.zh: 披萨外送。我来了，我来拿。

yingyinNormal.en: Okay, maybe check the delivery cost on those boots? Mm-hmm.
yingyinNormal.zh: 好吧，也许查看一下那双靴子的运费？嗯嗯。

yingyinNormal.en: Sounds like somebody wants to be Mr. Pizza Delivery Girl. Well…
yingyinNormal.zh: 看来有人想当披萨外送先生了。

yingyinNormal.en: Dom da-da dom. Here ye. Here ye. Delivery from the Mattress King.
yingyinNormal.zh: 听我说，听我说，床垫大王送货来了。

yingyinNormal.en: It is morning. And the Mr. Zebra the postman has a special delivery.
yingyinNormal.zh: 现在是清晨。斑马先生来送一个特别的包裹给佩奇家。

yingyinNormal.en: It is morning. And the Mr. Zebra the postman has a special delivery.
yingyinNormal.zh: 现在是清晨。斑马先生来送一个特别的包裹给佩奇家。

yingyinNormal.en: I'm thinking $400 per machine, for 50 units,paid at the time of delivery.
yingyinNormal.zh: 400美元订购50台，货到的时候付款。

yingyinNormal.en: Oh, sure. What's this? The delivery charge is almost as much as the couch.
yingyinNormal.zh: 没问题，这是什么？运费几乎跟价格一样贵。

yingyinNormal.en: This frenetic little dot is the delivery end of a vast and complicated machine.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这个快速移动的小点代表一个物流终端，这个巨大复杂机器的终点。

yingyinNormal.en: Why not? With online shopping and overnight delivery, I can get anything I want.
yingyinNormal.zh: 为什么不能？有网上购物和隔天送达，我要什么有什么。

yingyinNormal.en: We told four people at your office four different times for Mr. Bishop's delivery.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我们告诉了你公司四个人四个不同的运货时间。

yingyinNormal.en: Agreed. Diane, have them sent to Florrick-Agos/Associates. When can we expect delivery?
yingyinNormal.zh: 同意，戴安，请把卷宗寄至... 福瑞克&艾格斯律所。我们什么时候能收到啊？

yingyinNormal.en: What's going on? Chandler was hitting on the hot delivery girl. I was not and oh God, shh.
yingyinNormal.zh: 怎么了？钱德跟外送辣妹打情骂俏。我才没有，拜托，你也小声点。

yingyinNormal.en: And then, when you get home, maybe there'll be a special delivery package waiting for you.
yingyinNormal.zh: 当你回到家，可能有个特别的包裹等着你。

yingyinNormal.en: Your delivery. Thank you. Would you like a drink? No, thanks. I'm not staying. That's a shame.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你的快递。谢谢，要来杯喝的吗？不用了，谢谢，我马上就走。真可惜。

yingyinNormal.en: The antibody heads to the golgi apparatus. Here, it's packed up for delivery outside the cell.
yingyinNormal.zh: 抗体去往高基式体。在这里，它会被包装起来向细胞外运输。

yingyinNormal.en: Well, yes Ross, pressing my third nipple opens the delivery entrance to the magical land of Narnia.
yingyinNormal.zh: 只要压我的第三个乳头，就会开启纳尼亚王国（著名的儿童魔幻小说）之门。

yingyinNormal.en: It is my day off. But Zoey's got a very special delivery for a Miss Peppa pig. Here you are, Peppa.
yingyinNormal.zh: 今天我确实休息。但是佐伊有个特别的包裹一定要送，是给小猪佩奇的。这个给你，佩奇。

yingyinNormal.en: But your business card says you guarantee next-day delivery. Oh, you can't guarantee that guarantee?
yingyinNormal.zh: 但你们的名片上写着"保证第二天送货"啊，你不能保证名片上的"保证"吗？

yingyinNormal.en: Before the day is over, it will be poured, rolled, cooled, and stacked for delivery to the customer.
yingyinNormal.zh: 在一天时间内它会被灌，碾，然后冷却，然后发货给顾客。
